### GET all patients
GET http://localhost:4004/api/v1/patients

### GET single patient by id
GET http://localhost:4004/api/v1/patients/7b9095ff-2b70-48a0-82c9-c2f855363cbb

### POST add a patient to database
POST http://localhost:4004/api/v1/patients
Content-Type: application/json
##Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "John Doe Billing Account Test",
  "email": "Kafka@example.com",
  "address": "123 main street22",
  "dateOfBirth": "1995-09-09",
  "registeredDate": "2024-11-28"
}
